name: Snail man
description:
Snail Man is a traveler who travels all over the world and carries his house with him.  He takes everything he has and what he finds on the road with him.  This strange traveler wanders in a world where different societies hardly communicate at all, just for the pleasure of traveling.
This portrait was created handmade way by my unique style"multi-angle"
